original: Ögren, Olov Wilhelm, tandläkare, Göteborg, f. 29/6/02 i Lycksele, Väs-terb. 1., av kyrkoh. Erik Ö. o. Maria Sundberg. G. 31 m. Karin Berghem. Barn: Birgitta f. 34, Sten Erik 36, Margareta 44. — Stud:ex. i Härnösand 21, tysk tandläk. i Frankfurt am Main 29, sv. tandläk. 34. Praktik i Hudiksvall 34-3S, i Gbg sed. 36.
translated: Ögren, Olov Wilhelm, dentist, Gothenburg, b. 29/6/02 in Lycksele, Västerbotten County, son of priest Erik Ö. and Maria Sundberg. Married on 31 with Karin Berghem. Children: Birgitta b. 34, Sten Erik b. 36, Margareta b. 44. — Graduated from high school in Härnösand in 21, studied dentistry in Frankfurt am Main in 29, Swedish dentistry in 34. Practiced in Hudiksvall from 34-35, in Gothenburg since 36.
